org.puredata.processing

Class PureDataP5Base

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.puredata.processing.PureDataP5Base
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PdReceiver

    public abstract class PureDataP5Base
extends Object
implements PdReceiver
    Abstract base class for using libpd with Processing. It provides a wrapper for libpd that is in line with the general look and feel of Processing libraries. Subclasses will provide the connection between libpd and the audio platform, such as JACK.
    Author:
    Peter Brinkmann (peter.brinkmann@gmail.com)
